m <- lm(Date.Averages.BP ~ Distance..km., data = dm)
h_hat <- predict(m, newdata = data.frame(Distance..km. = dm$Distance..km.))
df <- data.frame(cbind(dm$Distance..km., dm$Date.Averages.BP, h_hat))
names(df) <- c("x", "y", "yhat")
df<-tbl_df(df)
df<-mutate(df,Site=dm$Site)
head(df)
